{
  "chapter": 297,
  "chapter_summary": "寇仲在怒海中游了整夜后精疲力竭爬上沙滩，真元接近油尽灯枯。一群海岛土著发现他，误以为是海贼，用农具攻击却被井中月刀鞘震退。土著少女能说生硬汉语，向寇仲求助对抗海贼，寇仲答应助阵。\n\n与此同时，徐子陵在大石寺跟真言大师学习九字真言手印。真言大师讲解佛家三密（身、口、意）的深义，演示不动根本印和大金刚轮印等九种基本手印，每种均有上百种印变。真言大师指出九字真言源自道家典籍《抱朴子》，说明佛道最终一家、真言重神不重形的道理。徐子陵心领神会，两手不自觉随地结出印式。\n\n寇仲醒来后发现功力不但恢复且尤胜从前，村民已逃离避难。远处有村落被焚烧，寇仲赶去救援。徐子陵化身为疤脸大侠行走在成都南市，追踪郑石如以证实其与阴癸派的关系，并计划将岳山来到成都的消息散播出去，诱出席应。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhen_yan_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "真言大师",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "佛家三密，是为身、口、意，实践与思维并重。身等于口，口等于意，意等于身，名虽分三，实为一如。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zhen_yan_da_shi",
      "text": "大师果是佛门高人，只寥寥几句话，就把堂内五百尊罗汉像背后的深义解释得一清二楚。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhen_yan_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "真言大师",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "老衲走遍天下，到今天才找到个像施主般一点便明的有缘人。施主可知以往当老衲说与别人知晓时，对方虽似听得头头是道，但却均非真的明白知道，更不用说用之于修行。往往得其身而失其口，取其意而弃其身。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zhen_yan_da_shi",
      "text": "大师怎知我不是口说明白，实则与其他人无异？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhen_yan_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "真言大师",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "适才老衲说出三密之秘时，施主十指不住微微晃动，可知密言入耳，意有所感，若非还不知真言奥义，说不定会喝几声给老袖听听。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zhen_yan_da_shi",
      "text": "自昨晚至今，我的手有点像不听指挥的样子，哈！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhen_yan_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "真言大师",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "人的肉身乃渡世的宝筏，内中蕴含天地之秘，我的九字真言手印，正是通过三密，通过人体而与宇宙沟通，达致天人合一之境，明心见性，即身成佛。那与出家在家并无半点关系，无论身体是否在袈裟之内，人就是人，不会变成其他东西。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zhen_yan_da_shi",
      "text": "大师这番话使小子茅塞顿开。不知是否性格使然，小子对空门教条重重，清规森严的生活方式提不起丝毫兴趣。总想若佛要相信他的人始能得证正果，那佛祖就太过霸道哩！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhen_yan_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "真言大师",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "施主想法独特，使老衲茅塞顿开才对。九字真言就是，嘿！不如就是'临兵斗者皆阵列在前'，这样施主会较易记牢。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zhen_yan_da_shi",
      "text": "甚么？九字真言竟就是大师现在随便想出来的九个字吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁人懂说汉语。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qie_sheng_sheng_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "怯生生少女",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你不是海贼吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_qie_sheng_sheng_shao_nv",
      "text": "我不但非是海贼，还是海贼的敌人。看！我就是因和海贼搏斗，才弄成这个样子的，哈！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qie_sheng_sheng_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "怯生生少女",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你肯助我们打海贼吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_qie_sheng_sheng_shao_nv",
      "text": "只要你们肯让我好好睡一觉，就算要去打天皇老子都可以。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhen_yan_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "真言大师",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "不要小看这九个字，乃来自东晋葛洪着的道家宝典《抱朴子》内卷的登涉篇，原文曰：'临兵斗者，皆阵列前行。常当视之，无所不辟。'",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zhen_yan_da_shi",
      "text": "我不解的非是指九字真言的出处来历，而是奇怪大师竟是临时想出来的，且大师乃佛门中人，为何却借用道家的典籍？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhen_yan_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "真言大师",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "老衲正要借此来向施主说明真言重神不重形，窍妙处乃三密的运用，佛道最后还不是一家。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zhen_yan_da_shi",
      "text": "小子受教啦！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zhen_yan_da_shi",
      "text": "厉害！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhen_yan_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "真言大师",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你察觉到甚么呢？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zhen_yan_da_shi",
      "text": "小子感到大师变成崇山峻岭，任谁都不能动摇大师分毫。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhen_yan_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "真言大师",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这正是不动根本印，手印虽千门万类，不动却是其中九种基本法式之一，所以今天老衲说的虽只是九种手印，事实上等若把所有手印一并传你，看。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhen_yan_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "真言大师",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "兵！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhen_yan_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "真言大师",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这是大金刚轮印，能为人驱魔治病，至于如何用于降魔卫道，就要靠施主自己啦！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qie_sheng_sheng_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "怯生生少女",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "还不快走，海贼真的来哩！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_qie_sheng_sheng_shao_nv",
      "text": "不用怕，万事有我顶着，我的刀子在那里？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qie_sheng_sheng_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "怯生生少女",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你未死过吗？快走！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 297,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    }
  ],
